    "# Convert Mileage into numerical form\n",
    "df[\"Mileage\"] = df[\"Mileage\"].str.replace(r\"([kmpl/g])\", \"\").astype(\"float\")"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 358,
   "id": "passive-gauge",
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "# Convert Power Column in numerical form\n",
    "df[\"Power\"] = df[\"Power\"].replace(\"null bhp\", 0)\n",
    "df[\"Power\"] = df[\"Power\"].str.replace(r\"([ bhp])\", \"\").astype(\"float\")\n",
    "\n",
    "mean_power = df[df[\"Power\"] != 0]\n",
    "df[\"Power\"] = df[\"Power\"].replace(0, mean_power[\"Power\"].mean())\n",
    "df[\"Power\"].fillna(mean_power[\"Power\"].mean(), inplace = True)"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 359,
   "id": "improving-return",
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [

    "df[\"New_Price\"] = df[\"New_Price\"].str.replace(r\"([LakhCr])\", \"\").astype(\"float\")\n",
    "df[\"New_Price\"].fillna(0, inplace = True)"
   ]

   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "id": "breeding-decrease",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "**Linear Regression (Kilometers | Price)**"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 481,
   "id": "conceptual-edgar",
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [
    {
     "data": {
      "image/png": "\n",
      "text/plain": [
       "<Figure size 1296x504 with 1 Axes>"
      ]
     },
     "metadata": {
      "needs_background": "light"
     },
     "output_type": "display_data"
    }
   ],
   "source": [
    "X = df[[\"Kilometers_Driven\"]]\n",
    "y = df[\"Price\"]\n",
    "\n",
    "lr = LinearRegression()\n",
    "\n",
    "lr.fit(X, y)\n",
    "\n",
    "y_hat = lr.predict(X)\n",
    "\n",
    "plt.figure(figsize = (18, 7))\n",
    "plt.scatter(X, y)\n",
    "plt.plot(X, y_hat, \"r\")\n",
    "plt.xlabel(\"Kilometers Driven\", size = 15)\n",
    "plt.ylabel(\"Price\", size = 15)\n",
    "plt.title(\"Used Car Price by Drive km\")\n",
    "plt.show()"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 482,
   "id": "fallen-separate",
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [
    {
     "name": "stdout",
     "output_type": "stream",
     "text": [
      "Root Mean Squared Error =  11.186248853695696\n",
      "Mean Absolute Error =  7.134568150876466\n",
      "R-Squared: =  0.00013208423899613297\n"
     ]
    }
   ],
   "source": [
    "# Performance\n",
    "print(\"Root Mean Squared Error = \", mean_squared_error(y, y_hat, squared=False))\n",
    "print(\"Mean Absolute Error = \", mean_absolute_error(y, y_hat))\n",
    "print(\"R-Squared: = \", r2_score(y, y_hat))"
   ]
